DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

92-1704. Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Shabazz.

Sito sponte, the second year of Donald A. Shabazz’s suspension will not be stayed and he will not be placed on probation until case No. 94-553, Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Shabazz, is disposed of and the Continuing Legal Education sanction is paid.

Pfeifer, J., dissents.
